POD1000000013_S0000050	That was a treat.
POD1000000013_S0000051	Yes.
POD1000000013_S0000052	privilege.
POD1000000013_S0000053	Yes.
POD1000000013_S0000054	It was a time of emerging from the office was changing from being the data protection commissioner, a kind of a registration function.
