POD1000000015_S0000207	it adds something to your being able to say, I am independent. What I think is unsatisfactory about it is, and probably the same for you, is the annuality of it.
POD1000000015_S0000208	It's very difficult to do proper business and resource planning when you can't guarantee you will have the money to do it next year.
