POD1000000015_S0000213	And that works well to the point we had some unexpected IT costs this year which we were able to go to the contingency fund.
POD1000000015_S0000214	but generally I think ombudsmen across the UK are underfunded.
POD1000000015_S0000215	If we had sufficient funding, we wouldn't have backlogs of cases, we would be doing things quicker.
POD1000000015_S0000216	but we have to make do with where we are at the moment.
POD1000000015_S0000217	Two final questions, Rosemary. First of all, going forward, what's your biggest challenge as the Ombudsman?
