POD1000000028_S0000240	But despite how well the tour was going, things behind the scenes were deteriorating for the Romanian coaches.
POD1000000028_S0000241	They could tell from the way officials were treating them that they were in danger of losing their jobs and their prestige.
POD1000000028_S0000242	We went there and we were treated very poorly from the very beginning of the tour. I mean, the president of the Gymnastics Federation gave us a cold shoulder.
