POD1000000030_S0000025	If New Balance, Alcony, others start competing with the same quality and performance of shoe and are charging $150, Nike's going to have to start dropping their cost down.
POD1000000030_S0000026	So it's just the natural how marketing works and it'll all come to an equilibrium over time.
