POD1000000030_S0000034	Well, if they're sponsored by Nike, they'll do all of their race pace work in those shoes.
POD1000000030_S0000035	But if they're buying their own shoes, what I typically see is they buy the pair, do maybe two workouts in them before the race, so they probably have about 15 to 20 miles on them, and then they do the race.
POD1000000030_S0000036	and then they'll maybe work out in those ones but buy a new pair before the next race they do.
POD1000000030_S0000037	And that's if it's someone that cares about saving a couple minutes on a marathon time.
