POD1000000035_S0000040	You know, if you're a state elected official and you have to budget a large amount of money for replacing a system, no user of that system initially benefits from it.
POD1000000035_S0000041	So you need to have the political will, which I think after this we will, to invest the money before problems happen, understanding that you're investing for the future.
