YOU1000000027_S0000023	or you're not just saying yes to people just because you're a people pleaser. A lot of times, for me personally, it's hard to say no. But in order to protect my energy and my well-being, I have to learn to say no more often.
YOU1000000027_S0000024	so that I don't find myself in those awkward situations where I'm doing something that I don't want to be doing, but I said yes, so I have to do it. And it just doesn't feel good. You don't want to put yourself in those situations.
