YOU1000000117_S0000018	they really suggest that a lot of our relationships success has to do with our expectations.
YOU1000000117_S0000019	And I think if anything, we might want to just be a little chiller about our expectations for our spouses than we might have been before.
YOU1000000117_S0000020	All of us are going through this struggling time. And so if you have a spouse who say, you know, didn't empty the dishwasher or isn't doing their part as much with kids.
