YOU1000000117_S0000076	And this is true for health care workers, but also service providers and even folks like who work at the grocery store who really have to give up and sacrifice right now to help other people.
YOU1000000117_S0000077	And this specific kind of meditation is what's known as loving-kindness meditation or metta.
