YOU1000000134_S0000086	They were at Stanford. Their professors had done this before. This is a pretty good bet. We might lose $100,000, but we could win big there.
YOU1000000134_S0000087	And at the time we had no company at all.
YOU1000000134_S0000088	And in fact, we couldn't cash the check.
YOU1000000134_S0000090	This is by the way with no legal documents, none of that stuff.
