YOU1000000134_S0000096	Enough money was $1 million, including $250,000 from Jeff Bezos of Amazon.com.
YOU1000000134_S0000098	Page and Brin incorporated Google on September 4th, 1998, and they moved into one of those storied garages in Menlo Park.
