YOU1000000170_S0000119	Through that Python workshop, I met people who offered me a job and from 1995, I mean, I went back to the Netherlands for a few months and then from 1995 to 2000,
YOU1000000170_S0000120	I worked in the US, in Northern Virginia at CNRI.
